    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Since the base Widget class has the `hold_sync` context manager, which delays the messages to the js side. How about `hold_trait_notifications`?\n\nBesides, in the case of the hold_sync context manager, there is an integer that is incremented to support holding multiple nested hold_sync.\n"
